SOFTWARE DEVELOPMENT AGENCY

Conceptzi Support your business foundation with adaptable software that improves key facets of your enterprise, set quality above all else, and make sure each solution we offer is top-notch; Our consistency, agile approach, and design-led solutions help organizations achieve more with less; enabling continuous evolvement to meet changing customer landscape, we do not compromise the quality, we do not waste time and deliver tangible results ASAP. We offer efficient cooperation saving time and money.

active Clients

Expert Team
Our Projects

We are committed to delivering the best customer experience with our remarkable services!

  • All
  • AI & Machine Learning
  • Enterprise Software Development
  • Web Application Development
Python Automation Tool

Python automation tool to gather working history of Employees working under any CEO from LinkedIn.

Sentiment Analysis Tool

Sentiment Analysis tool for a Chile Based startup “Sensla”. Data was scraped in Spanish language from multiple e-commerce websites which helped to train ML model using Tensorflow and Pytorch.

Data Visualization Tool

A Data visualization tool to gather CSV data from any source and display insights in the form of multiple charts. The web app was built using Bootstrap, Chart JS and Django.

Stock Screening Application

Stock screening application which helps to predict stock prices as well for the next day using statistical inference techniques. Web app was built using Django and Angular 8.

View All Projects
Trending Solution

Our team is experienced and knowledgeable in custom software development. we cover all latest technologies, our team is quick learn and we can easily adopt any new technology. We have worked with all latest platforms; we can cover all your requirements with any preferred platform. Conceptzi is one of the Best Salesforce/software Development Company, Best Python Development Company and Best AI Development Company.

// our clients

Drop Zone Automation

Let's Create Something Great
